---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../../../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
---

<Layout title="Exercise Stress Test — Dr Delhasse" description="The exercise stress test on a bicycle evaluates your heart's response to physical exertion." lang="en">

  <section class="hero-page">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumb items={[{label:'Home', href:'/en'}, {label:'Cardiac Examinations', href:'/en/cardiac-examinations'}, {label:'Exercise Stress Test'}]} />
      <h1>Exercise <span class="text-primary">Stress Test</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Cardiac ergometry</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container detail-content">
      <img src="/images/detail/epreuve-effort.webp" alt="Exercise stress test" class="detail-hero-img" />
      <img src="/images/svg/examens/Ergometria.svg" alt="Exercise stress test" class="detail-icon" />

      <p>The exercise stress test, or ergometry, is a key examination for evaluating your heart's response to physical exertion.</p>

      <p>The clinic performs this examination on a stationary bicycle while recording the electrocardiogram (ECG) in real time. The test identifies potential coronary artery disease through ECG changes during physical exertion that reveal possible arterial narrowing.</p>

      <p>Beyond cardiovascular screening, the stress test provides a comprehensive evaluation of fatigue, blood pressure and pulse evolution, and rhythm disorder monitoring.</p>

      <div class="detail-cta">
        <a href="/en/cardiac-examinations" class="btn btn--outline-dark">&larr; All examinations</a>
        <a href="/en/contact" class="btn btn--primary">Book an appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-page { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, #1a3d6d 100%); padding: 6rem 0 4rem; color: var(--color-white); }
  .hero-page h1 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: 2.75rem; }
  .hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .detail-content { max-width: 800px; }
  .detail-icon { width: 80px; height: 80px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-hero-img { width: 100%; height: 300px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .detail-content p { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-gray); }
  .detail-cta { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .hero-page h1 { font-size: 2rem; } }
</style>
